org.jivesoftware.smackx.muc.packet

Class MUCUser

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jivesoftware.smackx.muc.packet.MUCUser
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Element, ExtensionElement, NamedElement

    public class MUCUser
extends Object
implements ExtensionElement
    Represents extended presence information about roles, affiliations, full JIDs, or status codes scoped by the 'http://jabber.org/protocol/muc#user' namespace.

      • getDestroy

        public Destroy getDestroy()
        Returns the notification that the room has been destroyed. After a room has been destroyed, the room occupants will receive a Presence stanza(/packet) of type 'unavailable' with the reason for the room destruction if provided by the room owner.
        Returns:
        a notification that the room has been destroyed.
